query:
INSERT INTO map (
                gbx_mapuid, mapname, ap_author_id, created,
                author_medal_ms, gold_medal_ms, silver_medal_ms, bronze_medal_ms 
            )
            VALUES (
                $1, $2, $3, to_timestamp($4),
                $5, $6, $7, $8
            )
            ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
            RETURNING ap_map_id
